  "description": "Versioned single source of truth for high-risk generation. artifact_types = carrier forms that are high-risk regardless of tags; validator G6 matches them after case/separator normalization (whitespace, _ and - are ignored). risk_tags = declared risk semantics; each tag carries enforcement trigger bits mapped to rules: approval_required -> G6 (governance.approval_required must be true), consent_required -> G4 (at least one consent-bearing input), disclosure_required -> G8 (disclosure_policy.ai_generated_disclosure_required must be true). Tags are DECLARED by the plan author; omission is not statically detectable (external review is the backstop).",
